{"docs":[{"location":"","title":"EEDesktop","text":"<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"lp-meta\">{\"title\":\"EEDesktop\",\"facts\":[{\"label\":\"Type\",\"value\":\"Desktop\"},{\"label\":\"RBProjectVersion\",\"value\":\"2026.02\"},{\"label\":\"Bundle ID\",\"value\":\"com.example.eedesktop\"},{\"label\":\"Version\",\"value\":\"1.0.0\"},{\"label\":\"App menu bar\",\"value\":\"MainMenuBar\"},{\"label\":\"Is web project\",\"value\":\"False\"}],\"contents\":[{\"kind\":\"Class\",\"count\":4},{\"kind\":\"Menu Bar\",\"count\":1},{\"kind\":\"Module\",\"count\":1},{\"kind\":\"Page / Window\",\"count\":4},{\"kind\":\"Toolbar\",\"count\":1}]}</script>\n\n<!-- Featured images come from the selected template; featured_portrait.png may be a mobile placeholder. -->\n<p><picture class=\"featured\">\n  <source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"assets/featured_portrait.png\">\n  <img src=\"assets/featured.png\" alt=\"EEDesktop — featured\">\n</picture></p>"},{"location":"#entities","title":"Entities","text":"<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Kind</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: right;\">Members</th>\n<th>Super</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"pages/aboutwindow/\">AboutWindow</a></td>\n<td>Page / Window</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"classes/app/\">App</a></td>\n<td>Class</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">6</td>\n<td>DesktopApplication</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"pages/chartwindow/\">ChartWindow</a></td>\n<td>Page / Window</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"toolbars/customerdetailstoolbar/\">CustomerDetailsToolbar</a></td>\n<td>Toolbar</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"pages/customerdetailswindow/\">CustomerDetailsWindow</a></td>\n<td>Page / Window</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"classes/datapoint/\">DataPoint</a></td>\n<td>Class</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">7</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"pages/invoicedetailswindow/\">InvoiceDetailsWindow</a></td>\n<td>Page / Window</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"menus/mainmenubar/\">MainMenuBar</a></td>\n<td>Menu Bar</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">0</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"classes/ordersdatabase/\">OrdersDatabase</a></td>\n<td>Class</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">18</td>\n<td>SQLiteDatabase</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"classes/selectablepopupmenu/\">SelectablePopupMenu</a></td>\n<td>Class</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">3</td>\n<td>DesktopPopupMenu</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"classes/strings/\">Strings</a></td>\n<td>Module</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">1</td>\n<td>—</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Entity types that exist in the official Xojo API link to <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/index.html\">the Xojo documentation</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>"},{"location":"classes/app/","title":"App","text":"<p><code>Class</code> <code>Protected</code></p>\n<p><strong>Inherits:</strong> <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/user_interface/desktop/desktopapplication.html\">DesktopApplication</a>  </p>"},{"location":"classes/app/#event-handlers","title":"Event Handlers","text":""},{"location":"classes/app/#opening","title":"Opening","text":"<p><code>Public</code> <code>Event Handler</code></p>\n<pre><code>Sub Opening()</code></pre>\n\n<details class=\"source\"><summary>Source</summary>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub Opening()\n      Orders = OrdersDatabase.SetupNewDatabase\n\n      If Orders &lt;&gt; Nil Then\n        Orders.UpdateInvoiceDates\n        CustomerDetailsWindow.Show\n      Else\n        Quit\n      End If\n\n    End Sub</code></pre>\n\n</details>"},{"location":"classes/app/#properties","title":"Properties","text":""},{"location":"classes/app/#dberrorlogfile","title":"DBErrorLogFile","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>DBErrorLogFile As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/files/folderitem.html\">FolderItem</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/app/#logdatabase","title":"LogDatabase","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>LogDatabase As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/databases/sqlitedatabase.html\">SQLiteDatabase</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/app/#orders","title":"Orders","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Orders As <a href=\"../ordersdatabase/\">OrdersDatabase</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/app/#properties-internal","title":"Properties — internal","text":"<details class=\"internal\"><summary>Private / internal members</summary>\n\n### LaunchedOn\n\n`Private, Shared`\n\n<pre><code>LaunchedOn As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/datetime.html\">DateTime</a></code></pre>\n\n</details>"},{"location":"classes/app/#constants","title":"Constants","text":""},{"location":"classes/app/#keditclear","title":"kEditClear","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Const kEditClear As String = \"&amp;Delete\"</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/","title":"DataPoint","text":"<p><code>Class</code> <code>Protected</code></p>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#methods","title":"Methods","text":""},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#constructor","title":"Constructor","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub Constructor(value as Integer, shape as Integer = 0)\n  Self.Value = value\n  Self.Shape = shape\nEnd Sub</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#pointnearby","title":"PointNearby","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function PointNearby(x as integer, y as integer, tolerance as integer = 10) As Boolean\n  If Abs(x-Self.x) &lt; tolerance And Abs(y-Self.y) &lt; tolerance Then\n    Return True\n  End If\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#properties","title":"Properties","text":""},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#label","title":"Label","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Label As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/string.html\">String</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#shape","title":"Shape","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Shape As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/integer.html\">Integer</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#value","title":"Value","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Value As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/integer.html\">Integer</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#x","title":"X","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>X As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/integer.html\">Integer</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/datapoint/#y","title":"Y","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code>Y As <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/data_types/integer.html\">Integer</a></code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/","title":"OrdersDatabase","text":"<p><code>Class</code> <code>Protected</code></p>\n<p><strong>Inherits:</strong> <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/databases/sqlitedatabase.html\">SQLiteDatabase</a>  </p>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#methods","title":"Methods","text":""},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#addinvoice","title":"AddInvoice","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function AddInvoice(invoiceNum As String, invoiceDate As String, invoiceAmount As Currency, customerID As String) As Boolean\n  Try\n    Var invoice As New DatabaseRow\n    invoice.Column(\"InvoiceNo\").StringValue = invoiceNum\n    invoice.Column(\"InvoiceDate\").StringValue = invoiceDate\n    invoice.Column(\"InvoiceAmount\").CurrencyValue = invoiceAmount\n    invoice.Column(\"CustomerID\").StringValue = customerID\n\n    Self.AddRow(\"Invoices\", invoice)\n  Catch e As DatabaseException\n    Return False\n  End Try\n\n  Return True\n\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#addinvoiceitem","title":"AddInvoiceItem","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function AddInvoiceItem(code As String, quantity As Integer, invoiceNum As String) As Boolean\n  Try\n    Var invoiceRecord As New DatabaseRow\n\n    invoiceRecord.Column(\"InvoiceNo\").StringValue = invoiceNum\n    invoiceRecord.Column(\"ProductCode\").StringValue = code\n    invoiceRecord.Column(\"Quantity\").IntegerValue = quantity\n\n    Self.AddRow(\"InvoiceItems\", invoiceRecord)\n  Catch e As DatabaseException\n    Return False\n  End Try\n\n  Return True\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#canceltransaction","title":"CancelTransaction","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub CancelTransaction()\n  Self.RollbackTransaction\nEnd Sub</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#deleteinvoiceitems","title":"DeleteInvoiceItems","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function DeleteInvoiceItems(invoiceNum As String) As Boolean\n  Try\n    Var sql As String = \"DELETE FROM InvoiceItems WHERE InvoiceNo=?\"\n\n    Self.ExecuteSQL(sql, invoiceNum)\n  Catch e As DatabaseException\n    Return False\n  End Try\n\n  Return True\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#endtransaction","title":"EndTransaction","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub EndTransaction()\n  Self.CommitTransaction\nEnd Sub</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#findcustomersbyid","title":"FindCustomersByID","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function FindCustomersByID(ID As String) As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM Customers WHERE ID=? ORDER BY lastname, firstname\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, ID)\n\n  Return rs\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#findcustomersbyname","title":"FindCustomersByName","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function FindCustomersByName(Optional searchName As String) As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM Customers WHERE lastname LIKE ? OR firstname LIKE ? ORDER BY lastname, firstname\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, searchName + \"%\", searchName + \"%\")\n\n  Return rs\n\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getinvoicebynumber","title":"GetInvoiceByNumber","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetInvoiceByNumber(invoiceNum As String) As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM Invoices WHERE InvoiceNo=?\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, invoiceNum)\n\n  Return rs\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getinvoiceitemsforinvoice","title":"GetInvoiceItemsForInvoice","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetInvoiceItemsForInvoice(invoiceNum As String) As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM InvoiceItems INNER JOIN Products ON Products.Code = InvoiceItems.ProductCode WHERE InvoiceNo=?\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, invoiceNum)\n\n  Return rs\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getinvoicesforcustomer","title":"GetInvoicesForCustomer","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>Update the list of invoices to show invoices from the selected customer</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetInvoicesForCustomer(CustomerID As String) As RowSet\n  // Update the list of invoices to show invoices from the selected customer\n  Var rs As RowSet = SelectSQL(\"SELECT * FROM Invoices WHERE CustomerID=?\", CustomerID)\n\n  Return rs\n\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getinvoiceyears","title":"GetInvoiceYears","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>Determine how many unique years there are in the invoices table</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetInvoiceYears() As String()\n  // Determine how many unique years there are in the invoices table\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT DISTINCT substr(invoicedate, 1, 4) FROM invoices ORDER BY invoicedate DESC\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql)\n\n  Var years() As String\n\n  If rs &lt;&gt; Nil Then\n    For Each year As DatabaseRow In rs\n      years.Add(year.ColumnAt(0).StringValue)\n    Next\n    rs.Close\n  End If\n\n  Return years\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getmonthlyinvoicetotalsbyyear","title":"GetMonthlyInvoiceTotalsByYear","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>For the specified year, group the invoices by month and then sum the amounts for the month</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetMonthlyInvoiceTotalsByYear(year As String) As Double()\n  // For the specified year, group the invoices by month and then sum the amounts for the month\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT substr(invoicedate, 6, 2), sum(invoiceamount) FROM invoices WHERE substr(invoicedate, 1, 4)  = ? GROUP BY substr(invoicedate, 6, 2)  ORDER BY substr(invoicedate, 6, 2)\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, year)\n\n  Var amounts(11) As Double\n\n  If rs &lt;&gt; Nil Then\n    For Each total As DatabaseRow In rs\n      amounts(total.ColumnAt(0).IntegerValue - 1) = total.ColumnAt(1).IntegerValue\n    Next\n    rs.Close\n  End If\n\n  Return amounts\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getnextinvoicenumber","title":"GetNextInvoiceNumber","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetNextInvoiceNumber() As Integer\n  Var rs As RowSet\n  rs = Self.SelectSQL(\"SELECT Max(invoiceno) FROM Invoices\")\n\n  If rs &lt;&gt; Nil And Not rs.AfterLastRow Then\n    Return rs.ColumnAt(0).IntegerValue + 1\n  Else\n    Return 1001\n  End If\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getproductbycode","title":"GetProductByCode","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetProductByCode(code As String) As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM Products WHERE Code = ?\"\n  Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, code)\n\n  Return rs\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#getproducts","title":"GetProducts","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function GetProducts() As RowSet\n  Var sql As String = \"SELECT * FROM Products\"\n\n  Var rs As RowSet\n  rs = Self.SelectSQL(sql)\n\n  Return rs\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#setupnewdatabase","title":"SetupNewDatabase","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>The database file is copied to the App folder using a Build Automation step.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Shared Function SetupNewDatabase() As OrdersDatabase\n  // The database file is copied to the App folder using a Build Automation step.\n\n  Var msg As String\n\n  // Get to the database from Resources and copy\n  // to ApplicationSupport in EEData folder.\n  Var sourceDB As New FolderItem\n\n  Var eeDB As FolderItem = SpecialFolder.Resource(\"EddiesElectronics.sqlite\")\n  If eeDB &lt;&gt; Nil And eeDB.Exists Then\n    // Copy to AppData\n    Var eeData As FolderItem = SpecialFolder.ApplicationData.Child(\"EEData\")\n    If Not eeData.Exists Then\n      eeData.CreateFolder\n    End If\n\n    Var eeDestDB As FolderItem = eeData.Child(\"EddiesElectronics.sqlite\")\n    If eeDestDB.Exists Then eeDestDB.Remove\n\n    eeDB.CopyTo(eeDestDB)\n    sourceDB = New FolderItem(eeDestDB.NativePath, FolderItem.PathModes.Native)\n  End If\n\n  If sourceDB = Nil Or sourceDB.Exists = False Then\n    msg = \"Could not find EddiesElectronics.sqlite.\"\n    #If TargetDesktop Then\n      MessageBox(msg)\n    #ElseIf TargetWeb Then\n      App.AppendToDBErrorLog(msg)\n    #Endif\n\n    Return Nil\n  End If\n\n  // Create a blank, in-memory only database so the user can make changes without\n  // affecting the on disk database\n  Var orders As New OrdersDatabase\n  orders.DatabaseFile = sourceDB\n  If Not orders.Connect Then\n    msg = \"Could not connect to \" + sourceDB.Name\n    #If TargetDesktop Then\n      MessageBox(msg)\n    #ElseIf TargetWeb Then\n      App.AppendToDBErrorLog(msg)\n    #Endif\n\n    Return Nil\n  End If\n\n  Return orders\n\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#updateinvoice","title":"UpdateInvoice","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Function UpdateInvoice(invoiceNum As String, invoiceDate As String, invoiceTotal As Currency) As Boolean\n  Try\n    Var sql As String = \"SELECT InvoiceNo, CustomerID, InvoiceDate, InvoiceAmount FROM Invoices WHERE InvoiceNo=?\"\n    Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(sql, invoiceNum)\n\n    If rs &lt;&gt; Nil Then\n      rs.EditRow\n      rs.Column(\"InvoiceDate\").StringValue = invoiceDate\n      rs.Column(\"InvoiceAmount\").CurrencyValue = invoiceTotal\n\n      rs.SaveRow\n\n      rs.Close\n    End If\n  Catch e As DatabaseException\n    Return False\n  End Try\n\n  Return True\nEnd Function</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/ordersdatabase/#updateinvoicedates","title":"UpdateInvoiceDates","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>Update the invoice dates to a range in the last 4 years\nThis method gets a unique list of years in descending order.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub UpdateInvoiceDates()\n  'Update the invoice dates to a range in the last 4 years\n  'This method gets a unique list of years in descending order.\n\n  Try\n    'Get a unique list of years in descending order.\n    Var rs As RowSet = Self.SelectSQL(\"SELECT DISTINCT Substr(InvoiceDate, 1, 4) FROM Invoices ORDER BY InvoiceDate DESC\")\n    'Get the most recent year from that list\n    Var mostRecentYear As Integer = rs.ColumnAt(0).IntegerValue\n    Var today As DateTime = DateTime.Now\n    'Determine the number of years between the current year and the most recent year in the database\n    Var delta As Integer = today.Year - mostRecentYear\n    'Loop through each year in the list of unique years\n    For Each row As DatabaseRow In rs\n      'Get the year from the list of unique years\n      Var year As Integer = rs.ColumnAt(0).IntegerValue\n      'Create a new year by adding the calculated delta to that year\n      Var newYear As Integer = year + delta\n      'Update all invoices by replacing the year with the new year\n      Var sql As String\n      sql = \"UPDATE Invoices SET InvoiceDate = REPLACE(InvoiceDate, '\" + year.ToString + \"-', '\" + newYear.ToString + \"-')\"\n      Self.ExecuteSQL(sql)\n    Next\n\n  Catch error As DatabaseException\n    System.Beep\n    MessageBox(\"A database exception occurred in the UpdateInvoiceDates method.\")\n  End Try\nEnd Sub</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/","title":"SelectablePopupMenu","text":"<p><code>Class</code> <code>Protected</code></p>\n<p><strong>Inherits:</strong> <a href=\"https://documentation.xojo.com/api/user_interface/desktop/desktoppopupmenu.html\">DesktopPopupMenu</a>  </p>"},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#event-definitions","title":"Event Definitions","text":""},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#_1","title":"SelectablePopupMenu","text":"<p><code>Event Definition</code></p>\n<pre><code>Event Open()</code></pre>\n\n<details class=\"source\"><summary>Source</summary>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Event Open()</code></pre>\n\n</details>"},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#event-handlers","title":"Event Handlers","text":""},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#opening","title":"Opening","text":"<p><code>Public</code> <code>Event Handler</code></p>\n<pre><code>Sub Opening()</code></pre>\n\n<details class=\"source\"><summary>Source</summary>\n\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub Opening()\n      Open\n\n    End Sub</code></pre>\n\n</details>"},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#methods","title":"Methods","text":""},{"location":"classes/selectablepopupmenu/#selectvalue","title":"SelectValue","text":"<p><code>Public</code></p>\n<p>Search for the specified value in the list and select it.\nIf no value is found then nothing is selected.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xojo\">Sub SelectValue(value As String)\n  // Search for the specified value in the list and select it.\n  // If no value is found then nothing is selected.\n  For i As Integer = 0 To Self.RowCount - 1\n    If Self.RowValueAt(i) = value Then\n      Self.SelectedRowIndex = i\n      Return\n    End If\n  Next\n\n  Self.SelectedRowIndex = -1\n\n  Return\nEnd Sub</code></pre>"},{"location":"classes/strings/","title":"Strings","text":"<p><code>Module</code> <code>Protected</code></p>"},{"location":"classes/strings/#constants","title":"Constants","text":""},{"location":"classes/strings/#about","title":"About","text":"<p><code>Protected</code></p>\n<pre><code>Const About As String, Dynamic = \"About\"</code></pre>"},{"location":"database/","title":"Databases","text":"<p>Schema documentation generated from explicitly selected database files.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Database</th>\n<th>Dialect</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: right;\">Tables</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: right;\">Columns</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: right;\">Relationships</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"eddieselectronics/\">EddiesElectronics</a></td>\n<td>sqlite</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">22</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: right;\">3</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"},{"location":"database/eddieselectronics/","title":"EddiesElectronics data dictionary","text":"<ul>\n<li>Dialect: <code>sqlite</code></li>\n<li>Source: <code>EddiesElectronics.sqlite</code></li>\n<li>Tables: 4</li>\n<li>Views: 0</li>\n<li>Relationships: 3</li>\n</ul>"},{"location":"database/eddiesel